article_title: Here are the results – The Denver Post
article_text:
People know where South Korea. 62.1% of people who played our South Korea map game got it right, which is just shy of the 63.9% of people who got Iran right, but is still totally respectable. Were you one of those 62.1%? Good job. Were you not? That’s okay too.
